<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-2875] Type 1 fonts are embedded incorrectly</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2875</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When embedding a Type 1 font, the Widths array is invalid, because the codes are ordered based on the order of the named glyphs in the font file, instead of in encoding order.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Additionally, there&apos;s an NPE because no GlyphList is set for a newly embedded PDType1Font.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There&apos;s also no way to choose the encoding, it&apos;s always taken from the AFM file.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
